  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ECCD Programme</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The aim of the Early Childhood Care and Development (ECCD) project is to put into place a more integrated initiative that seeks to make significant improvements in the early childhood sector. The overall strategy will aim to introduce a holistic and sustainable early childhood development and education system using community based approaches which include strengthening the capacity of parents and community leaders; raise public awareness on the importance of ECCD; build capacity of ECCD facilitators; in addition to evaluating and documenting good practices. Partnerships and linkages with other sectors will be an important component of this initiative to ensure that health  nutrition  protection  education  psychosocial well-being and other developmental needs of younger children are addressed and catered for.</narrative>
  </description>
